Package: OrdPower
Type: Package
Title: Power Analysis and Sample Size Planning for Longitudinal Data
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(person("Sijing", "Shao", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                     email = "sshao2@nd.edu"),
              person("Ziqian", "Xu", role = "aut"),
              person("Ross", "Jacobucci", role = "aut"))
Author: Sijing Shao [aut, cre], Ziqian Xu [aut], Ross Jacobucci [aut]
Maintainer: Sijing Shao <sshao2@nd.edu>
Description: Provides the pipelines for power analysis of longitudinal models with ordinal outcome variables using a simulation-based approach. Users can specify different sample sizes, timepoints, skewness of effects etc. when performing power analysis.
